description:
It is our mission to help people to prepare for uncertain times by growing our own food. As we have been helping fellow Christians the opportunity was given to help someone of another faith. Although she was not interested in the books we offered her, the seed was sown. We pray another to water and God will give the increase. Please reach out to us if you are near the Georgia area and are interested in starting a garden or are looking for tips to improve. We will be happy to assist in any way we can.
Happy Planting!
Contact us @ gardenevangelist@gmail.com
